  <body>
    <section name="About Termmap">
      <p>The PDS4 Terminological Mapping tool (Termmap) maps a PDS3 keyword to its equivalent or closedly matched counterpart in PDS4.  This appplication also provides a web service to search for pds4 records using a pds3 keyword or vice versa.
      </p>

      <p>Please send comments, change requests and bug reports to the <a href="mailto:pds_operator@jpl.nasa.gov">PDS Operator</a> at pds_operator@jpl.nasa.gov.
      </p>
    </section>
